The paper deals with planning and learning in multiagent POMDPs, which involves artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and multiagent systems (cs.MA). The proposed approach is based on value functions, which is a common topic in machine learning (cs.LG). The scalability aspect of the approach is also relevant to robotics (cs.RO) and control systems (cs.SY).
